NUMBER 2848
NAME Fire Pit
FIXED_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Flaky pieces of ash drift upwards in the heat rising from the fire blazing in
a large rock-rimmed circular pit. Not a single pebble or rock disturbs the
absolutely smooth ground which is covered with a fine layer of soft soil.
Carved oak benches have been place safely away from the burning embers, though
close enough to still bathe anyone resting upon them in the warm of the flames.
*DESCRIPTION_END
