NUMBER 3811
NAME Underground Home
FIXED_LIGHT
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Polished rosewood paneling forms the interior walls of this spacious
underground home. A skillfully woven rug in rich hues covers the floor,
preventing any dust from touching the enormous stuffed silk pillows
which are mounded against the walls. Fireflies blink on and off as they
zip around the ceiling which is filled with fragrant boughs of pine and
enclosed by an emormous piece of netting.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT O 2851
;
NUMBER 2856
NAME Camp's Waterfall
FIXED_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Tiny green frogs croak and hop for cover beneath the lush ferns that grow
in almost every crack and crevice between the jutting mountain wall forming
an enormous waterfall. Rushing water plummets down a huge natural funnel
between the rocks, speeding downwards to a large pool which is only partially
visible here. Brightly burning torches, mounted on stout wooden beams, sputter
occasionally as they are doused by water droplets. A sturdy wooden cage,
attached to a maze of ropes and pullies extending up the rocky wall, dangles
only a few feet off the ground and exactly matches another cage perched at
the very top of the falls.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT SW 2851
ITEM 1 661 ADJ1=740
ITEM 2 361 ADJ1=1225 ADJ2=355
