NUMBER 2857
NAME Top of Waterfall
FIXED_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
A fine mist sprays continuously from the water gushing forth from the side of
the sheer mountain wall only a few feet away. Candles flicker inside the two
enormous clear paned lanterns hung from metal rods pounded into the rock. The
stone beneath the stream of water rushing downwards appears very smooth and
slick and free of any debris. A sturdy wooden cage dangles a few feet away,
though too far for you to be able to reach it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
