NUMBER 3805
NAME Bottom of Waterfall
FIXED_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Water splashes and crashes all around you, as you find yourself emersed in
a small pool beneath the waterfall. Tender-leafed ferns and smoking torches
outline the shoreline. It is impossible to see the pond floor through the
churning water. You realize that you had better move quickly or someone
might crash down on top of you!
*DESCRIPTION_END
