ENDIF
;
NUMBER 3812
NAME Base of Waterfall
FIXED_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Sputtering torches, tender-leafed ferns and wildflowers circle the perimeter
of a small pool at the base of a stunning waterfall. Water crashes into
the pond, whipping the surface into a froth and spattering the rocks. The
large gray toads which peek occasionally from their hiding spots in the
crevices don't seem at all perturbed by the constant roar and pounding water.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 2851
